<P>
Orville Schell's piece on Fang Lizhi was enthralling. 
</P>
<P>
FREDERICK WAKEMAN 
</P>
<P>
DIRECTOR, INSTITUTE OF EAST ASIAN STUDIES 
</P>
<P>
UC Berkeley 
</P>
</TEXT>
