<HEADLINE>
<P>
AUCTIONS: LOS ANGELES COUNTY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEVERLY HILLS: Eleven condominiums at Villa Gale, by Bob Margolis; 
1-2-bedrooms, 1 3/4-2 1/2-baths, 1,345-2,220 square feet; minimum bids, 
$250,000-$470,000; office open Thursday-Sunday, 10 a.m.-7 p.m. at 235 S. Gale 
Ave.; on-site auction to be held Dec. 6 at 8 p.m. 
</P>
<P>
CALABASAS: Twenty-one townhomes at Calabasas Colony, by Amper Development; 
2-4-bedrooms, 2 1/2-baths, 1,392-2,428 square feet; minimum bids, 
$150,000-$230,000; office open 10 a.m.-noon today at 5340 Las Virgenes Road; 
auction scheduled for 3 p.m. today at Warner Center Hilton, 6360 Canoga Ave., 
Woodland Hills. 
</P>
<P>
CHATSWORTH: Two custom homes and 15 homesites at Summit Ridge, by Rans Bottom 
Corp.; homes have 5 bedrooms and 5 1/2 baths, with minimum bids of $875,000; 
sites are one-half to 2 acres, with minimum bids of $250,000-$683,000; sales 
office open 10 a.m.-6 p.m. daily at 22436 N. Summit Ridge Circle; auction to be 
held on-site at 1 p.m. on Dec. 3. 
</P>
<P>
