<P>
My family and I were totally enamored of the Disney Channel movie "Back to 
Hannibal." At first I was a bit apprehensive at the idea of seeing Tom Sawyer, 
Huckleberry Finn and Mark Twain's other characters as adults, but the movie won 
us over with it wonderful story and performances. 
</P>
<P>
Michele Edison, Los Angeles 
