<P>
AND FINALLY: Expect PolyGram to announce its label reorganization plan as early 
as next week, with up-and-coming exec Ed Eckstine running Mercury Records and 
newly hired Rick Dobbis heading up PLG Records, which will encompass the 
Polydor, London and Smash labels. 
