<HEADLINE>
<P>
CSUN WOMEN RALLY, ONLY TO LOSE, 60-52 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Southwest Texas women's basketball team held off Cal State Northridge to 
emerge with a 60-52 victory in a consolation-round game of the Fullerton 
tournament Saturday. 
</P>
<P>
The Matadors (0-2) closed to 55-50 with 1 1/2 minutes left after trailing, 
34-14, but could get no closer. 
</P>
</TEXT>
