<P>
Game Story 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA112590-0140 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 313302 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
November 25, 1990, Sunday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 18; Column 3; Sports Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
81 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
O.C. PLAYERS ELIMINATED FROM GOLF TOURNAMENT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
TUCSON 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
