Woods, who had won his opening round match against Eric Dollenberg of 
Flourtown, Pa., 2 and 1, was eliminated by Grant Masson of Richardson, Tex., 3 
and 2. 
</P>
<P>
Booth, the qualifying medalist, defeated Jo Jo Robertson of Roswell, N.M., 2 
and 1, but was beaten by Heather Bowie of Edmond, Okla., 4 and 2. 
</P>
