</P>
<P>
The Tritons' victory, their second two-point decision in as many nights, was 
safe after the Hawks' Vernaldo Butler missed a three-point attempt at the 
buzzer. Butler led all scorers with 35 points. 
</P>
<P>
Rapp, Shawcroft and Butler were joined on the all-tournament team by UCSD's 
Gordon McNeill and Christian Heritage's Jeff Martin. 
</P>
<P>
