</P>
<P>
Point Loma Nazarene defeated Cal State San Bernardino in a nonconference game 
at Point Loma, 114-99. Donnie Buettner led the Crusaders with 25 points and 16 
rebounds, while Mark Bulgin had 24 points and Rusty Fallin 18. PLNC led 58-41 
at halftime and improved to 2-1, while CSUSB dropped to 1-3. 
</P>
