aging buildings that city officials want to spruce up. ; Photo, Southbound 
train rolls along Long Beach Boulevard near 14th Street, an area that long 
thrived with car dealers and auto-related businesses. RICK CORRALES / Los 
Angeles Times; Map, LONG BEACH BOULEVARD PROJECT AREA, Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
