RESERVOIR COMPLETION DATE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A reservoir under construction at 253 W. Harriet St. is expected to be 
completed by April, said Camille Dudley, chairwoman of the Town Council's Land 
Use Committee. 
</P>
<P>
The reservoir, which will cost nearly $900,000, is being built by the Foothill 
Municipal Water District and will serve all of Altadena. 
</P>
