<CORRECTION>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
<P>
Beijing meeting -- Because of an editing error, The Times reported incorrectly 
on Nov. 25, in a special section entitled The Line in the Sand, that Assistant 
Secretary of State Richard H. Solomon discussed the gulf crisis in Beijing last 
August with Chinese Premier Li Peng. In fact, Solomon met with Deputy Foreign 
Minister Tian Zengpei and not with the premier. 
</P>
</CORRECTION>
